{"tid":1441794,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"求文宣組，可唔可以整一張不割席圖片","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T18:22:49.000Z","uid":245968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f38a75d62add8ec88418e937f1f7f58059882be","tid":1441794,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"眼見太多分化，唔可以再咁落去<br />\n<br />\n有一段藍絲片點醒咗我<br />\n<br />\n個仆街話我哋只係代表香港一小撮人<br />\n<br />\n想文宣組整一張係關於我哋放核武都唔割<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n「勇武代表我，抗爭代表我」<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港，死都唔割」<br />\n<br />\n小弟整唔到好似你哋嗰種震撼感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5f083bd079fe317231971718c7558e2ee56be4","tid":1441794,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:58:20.000Z","msg":"5大訴求<br />\n真普選"},{"pid":"03f791565d35c1b8af57e198eed92d478bfa8561","tid":1441794,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:22:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}